								<span>&amp;nbsp;<span>2. Interest on overdue accounts is chargeable @ 18%p.a.</span></span><br/>
								<span>&amp;nbsp;<span>3. All dispute are subjected to jurisdiction of the courts in Pune.</span></span>
								</td>
					            <td class="text-center" style="font-size: medium;" colspan="6"><b>FOR ACS GLOBAL VENTURES</b><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><b>Authorised Signature</b></td>
					        </tr>
						<!--/tbody-->
					</table>
			</div>	
						
	</t>
	</t>
